@Raptor - The last 20 or so lines of the log file refer to an inability to find a PartModule of typename "ModuleEngineConfigs", and one part from AIES (what is showing during startup when it hangs) is unable to find a PartModule of typename "ModuleEnginesRF". Actually, all of those errors refer to AIES parts. The last two "paragraphs" of the log file do appear to be an error with SolverEngines.ModuleAnimateEmissive.<br>
<br>
@Starwaster - I actually did try removing SolverEngines.dll from RealFuels/plugins, though to no avail. Although, based on the errors in the log file, it would appear that the problems do stwm from a combination of SolverEngines, ModuleAnimateEmissive, and SolverEngines (or Real Fuels).
